<h2 id="key-innovations">Key Innovations</h2>

<p><strong>Smart Data Visualization:</strong>
Created interactive charts that automatically adjust complexity based on user expertise level, making financial data accessible to beginners while providing depth for professionals.</p>

<p><strong>Intelligent Filtering System:</strong>
Built natural language processing for ETF search, allowing users to find investments using plain English queries like “low-cost European tech funds.”</p>

<p><strong>Performance Optimization:</strong>
Implemented advanced caching strategies and lazy loading to handle large financial datasets without compromising user experience.</p>

<h2 id="technologies-used">Technologies Used</h2>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Frontend</strong>: React.js, D3.js for visualizations, Material-UI</li>
  <li><strong>Backend</strong>: Node.js, Express.js, PostgreSQL</li>
  <li><strong>Real-time</strong>: WebSocket connections, Redis for caching</li>
  <li><strong>Infrastructure</strong>: AWS deployment, CloudFront CDN</li>
  <li><strong>Analytics</strong>: Custom tracking for user behavior analysis</li>
  <li><strong>Testing</strong>: Jest, Cypress for end-to-end testing</li>
</ul>

